		<title>貓咪炸毛行為大解密！牠到底是恐懼、生氣還是興奮？</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/11/%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e7%82%b8%e6%af%9b%e8%a1%8c%e7%82%ba%e5%a4%a7%e8%a7%a3%e5%af%86%ef%bc%81%e7%89%a0%e5%88%b0%e5%ba%95%e6%98%af%e6%81%90%e6%87%bc%e3%80%81%e7%94%9f%e6%b0%a3%e9%82%84%e6%98%af%e8%88%88/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 11 Sep 2025 05:58:36 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
